<section class="grid full block clearfix">
	<div class="px4 px4-2 py4 center block clearfix mxa">
		<p class="h4 regular">CoderDojo is a free coding class covering everything from basic HTML & CSS, to JavaScript, game development, and web programming. Our Dojo welcomes anyone ages 6â€“16 years old.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="bt-light-gray">
<%= render partial: "lessons/lesson", object: @lesson if @lesson.present? %>
</section>

<section class="full block clearfix mt2 py2">
	<h2 class="h2 regular mb1 center">Class time and location</h2>
	<p class="center px1">Classes last about 3 hours and are held on Saturday's at the <a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a> San Francisco office.</p>

	<div class="left two-thirds block mxa py1">
		<iframe width="100%" height="420" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" src="https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=2nd+street+and+brannan+st&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.763658,-122.437477&amp;sspn=0.169904,0.308647&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Brannan+St+%26+2nd+St,+San+Francisco,+California+94107&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;ll=37.78185,-122.392099&amp;output=embed"></iframe><br /><small><a href="https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=2nd+street+and+brannan+st&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.763658,-122.437477&amp;sspn=0.169904,0.308647&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Brannan+St+%26+2nd+St,+San+Francisco,+California+94107&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;ll=37.78185,-122.392099" style="text-align:left">View Larger Map</a></small>
	</div>
	<div class="left one-third block mxa py1">
		<h3 class="h4 regular">Time</h3>
		<p class="mb1">Saturday's, 10am-1pm</p>

	<h3 class="h4 regular">Location</h3>
	<p class="mb1">88 Colin P Kelly Jr St,<br />
	San Francisco, CA 94107</p>

	<h3 class="h4 regular">What to bring</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Your ticket</li>
		<li>A packed lunch</li>
		<li>A laptop with Chrome and a text editor installed on it</li>
		<li>A parent! (Very important). If you are 13 or under, your parent must stay with you during the session</li>
	</ul>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="grid py2 full block clearfix bt-light-gray bb-light-gray">
	<div class="full block mxa clearfix">
		<div class="grid half block py1 mxa">
			<h2 class="regular h3">Register for updates</h2>
        <p class="f2 mr3">Sign up to our mailing list to keep up to date with planned classes.</p>
        <%= form_tag '/newsletters/announcements', method: 'post', remote: true, id: 'newsletter', class: 'newsletter-form mt1' do %>
          <%= email_field_tag 'email', nil, placeholder: 'Email address', class: 'js-newsletter-input' %>
          <%= submit_tag 'Register', class: 'btn js-newsletter-submit' %>
          <p class="mt1 small mid-gray hide js-newsletter-result">&nbsp;</p>
        <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="grid half block py1 mxa">
      <h2 class="regular h3">Get involved</h2>
        <p class="f2 mr3">If you are interested in being a mentor or teaching a class please get in touch.</p>
        <p class="mt1"><a href="mailto:sanfran@coderdojo.com">Email us</a></p>
    </div>
	</div>
</section>

